strings.Value: "Maybe, if we pick up and move right now, he will fall behind and leave us in peace? Does somebody else like this plan like I do?"
"Do not yawn in my direction, goblin. The stench of your breath can knock out some Shelyn followers!"
"When you yawn like that and rub your eyes, you look like a child! Small... carnivorous... hideous child."
"Bhahahaha, look at him! So exhausted he's about to plant himself in the ground!"
